{
  "title": "Garlicky Dense Irish Noodles Bowl",
  "description": "A vegan Irish-inspired dish featuring vermicelli rice noodles, garlic, and a variety of spices, perfect for a quick and energizing meal. This recipe is suitable for a Buddhist temple food service.",
  "cuisine": "Irish",
  "diet": [
